name: Mental Health, Service Provide
what_you_do: Melissa Fox is a trauma-informed transition and growth coach who helps individuals navigate personal transformations and major life transitions by clarifying their vision, setting goals, and unlocking their full potential.
who_you_serve: Melissa serves individuals who are experiencing transitions in their lives, including career shifts and personal transformations, particularly those feeling stuck or overwhelmed due to past trauma.
bio: Certified Clinical Trauma Professional, trained in various therapeutic modalities, extensive experience in psychology and coaching.
